===Hiragana character===
'''гҒ„''' (''i'')

# the [i] phoneme, typically in words of Japanese origin
#: The second character of first column of the [[hiragana]] [[syllabary]], it is analogous to [[гӮӨ]] (''i'') in the [[katakana]] syllabary. The previous hiragana character is [[гҒӮ]] and the next is [[гҒҶ]] (''u'').

